{
  "texts": [
    "Section 5 presents a case study on the use of Impromptu to build a prompt library to evaluate ethical biases in large language models (LLMs).",
    "After that, Sect. 6 analyzes how MDE can contribute to the field of prompt engineering.",
    "In Sect. 7, we draw the conclusions and identify future avenues of research.",
    "Related workThe massive impact of the input prompt on the output of a generative AI system has triggered the creation of a myriad of prompting tools, guides and strategies to help craft the right prompt for the task at hand.",
    "In this section, we summarize these different initiatives and compare them with our proposal."
  ]
}